'''PENTA''' is a German esports organization formed after the merger of a couple of smaller esports organizations in 2013. They were previously known as '''PENTA Sports''' and '''PENTA'''. On the 21st January 2019, the organisation announced a partnership with '''TSV 1860 Munich''' and a rebranding to '''PENTA 1860'''.

